ZH: 我们坐大巴去旅行。
EN: We are taking a coach to go on a trip.

ZH: 大巴上的座位很舒适。
EN: The seats on the coach are very comfortable.

ZH: 今天大巴上没有空座位了。
EN: There are no empty seats on the coach today.

ZH: 每辆大巴都有空调。
EN: Every coach has air conditioning.

ZH: 我们从机场坐大巴去市中心。
EN: We took a coach from the airport to the city center.

ZH: 大巴司机很热情。
EN: The coach driver is very friendly.

ZH: 大巴要在十分钟后出发。
EN: The coach will depart in ten minutes.

ZH: 大巴停在车站前面。
EN: The coach is parked in front of the bus station.

ZH: 大巴上有免费的WIFI。
EN: There is free WIFI on the coach.

ZH: 我们买了大巴的往返票。
EN: We bought round-trip tickets for the coach.

ZH: 大巴从一座城市到另一座城市需要五个小时。
EN: It takes five hours for the coach to travel from one city to another.

ZH: 大巴的速度比火车慢。
EN: Coaches are slower than trains.

ZH: 大巴的站台在哪里？
EN: Where is the coach stop?

ZH: 我们将在九点钟乘坐大巴。
EN: We will take the coach at nine o'clock.

ZH: 大巴是最便宜的出行方式之一。
EN: Coaches are one of the cheapest modes of transportation.

ZH: 星期天的大巴班次很少。
EN: There are few coach services on Sundays.

ZH: 我们将跳上一辆驶向南方的大巴。
EN: We will hop onto a coach heading south.

ZH: 大巴上的乘客大部分都是旅行者。
EN: Most of the passengers on the coach are travelers.

ZH: 大巴在下一个城市停下来让乘客下车。
EN: The coach stops in the next city to let passengers off.

ZH: 我们的大巴已经迟到了半小时。
EN: Our coach is already half an hour late.
